  ID: MalteseSoldier2
  Name: "Andr\xE9"
  Icon: {fileID: 409668665, guid: 4147f2bc6fccc974f937adc9cd1a5700, type: 3}
  Description: "Wound: Cannonball crushed his leg above the knee \u2014 dangling
    flesh and splintered bone remain.\n\nStory: Andr\xE9, a young page barely sixteen,
    grips your arm with surprising strength despite his pallor. His first battle
    has left him mutilated before he even learned to shave. He sobs that his mother
    gave him a wooden cross to keep him safe \u2014 now it lies splintered in the
    mud beside what remains of his leg.\n\n\nRequired bandages to heal: 2"
